{"type": "article", "id": 6058, "title": "Drawer Table 书桌", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-10T07:47:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234005UsgI8JzYVSofdK7R.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰设计师 Ineke Hans 日前为荷兰家具品牌 Arco 设计了一款名为「Drawer Table」的书桌，亮相 2015 德国科隆国际家具展。 Ineke Hans 对传统的带抽屉式的餐桌进行重新了思考和更新，考虑到了现代人的生活习惯。比如，我们每天都有很多时间是在桌子前度过的，吃饭、看书、工作或是休闲游戏等等， Ineke Hans 意欲为其提供用户在做上述这些事情时存放纸巾、电脑、纸笔等收纳需求，配合轻薄的桌面，在推拉抽屉时也不会制造过多噪音，为腿部留出舒适可活动的空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234003CyhWwEIaJtSxPRfc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234003If9oZ1bOm0pjAgys.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234004PBkjzmXKEGclCear.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052340048FsPVhaL6Tu9piyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}